import sys
sys.path.insert(0, '/workspace')
from functools import reduce
import operator
from django.db.models.lookups import Exact
from django.db.models.expressions import Case, When, Value, CombinedExpression
from django.db.models.expressions import Combinable

children = [Exact(Value(1), Value(1)), Exact(Value(1), Value(1)), Exact(Value(1), Value(1))]
# build rhs_sum similar to where.py
rhs_sum = reduce(
    operator.add,
    (Case(When(c, then=1), default=0) for c in children),
)
rhs_mod = rhs_sum % 2
print('rhs_sum type:', type(rhs_sum))
print('rhs_mod type:', type(rhs_mod))
try:
    is_combined = isinstance(rhs_mod, CombinedExpression)
    print('is CombinedExpression?', is_combined)
    connector = getattr(rhs_mod, 'connector', None)
    print('connector repr:', repr(connector))
    if connector == Combinable.MOD:
        print('PASS')
    else:
        print('FAIL: connector not MOD')
except Exception as e:
    print('ERROR', e)
    raise
